IMF’s Blanchard Issues ‘Call to Arms’ to European Policy Makers

-- B y   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 
2011-09-20T13:34:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/imf-s-blanchard-issues-call-to-arms-to-european-policy-makers.html
International Monetary Fund chief
economist  Olivier Blanchard  said today that he was issuing a
“call to arms” to European policy makers and said  Europe  must
“get its act together.”   He spoke at a news conference in  Washington  following the
release of the IMF’s World Economic Outlook.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sandrine Rastello in Washington at 
 srastello@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kevin Costelloe at 
 kcostelloe@bloomberg.net  